name: Youkai Strike!!
description:
A bouncing brawl!  Three teams come forward to take on the fairy hoards!  Can all three teams complete the challenge?  They each only get one chance each!

A small spoof of the mobile game Monster Strike, but with Touhou characters.

Made in 72 hours for the Touhou Fan Game Jam 2.

Huge shoutouts to Rida. (@pudarida) for doing the art!  Go check out her stuff!  She's awesome!
